  Transform your bedroom with the Urbanzo Full Elastic Bed Ruffle. This elegant bed skirt is crafted from premium quality 1000 Thread Count Egyptian Cotton, offering unmatched comfort and a refined appearance. Its 3-sided ruffle design features a tailored hem that adds a touch of sophistication, while the elastic wrap around system simplifies the process of changing your bed skirt. No more struggling to lift the mattress – this design allows for effortless installation and removal, making it the perfect addition to your bedroom for a timeless and classy aesthetic.
  The Urbanzo Full Elastic Bed Ruffle is ideal for those looking to enhance both the functionality and style of their bedding setup. The 21-inch drop ensures a full coverage over most box springs, while the fade-resistant fabric maintains its vibrant look over time. Perfectly suited for beds with footboards or bed posts, this ruffle adds a refined and classic touch to any room. Its easy care properties make it a great choice for everyday use, keeping your bedding looking pristine with minimal effort.
